    %h3 Nerdboat 2013

    %figure
      = image_tag 'nerdboat.jpg'

    %p
      Arr, matey! Join Florian and his crew and let a hacker's dream come true: 30
      = link_to 'developers, designers, web hackers and tinkerers', 'https://twitter.com/nerdboat/nerdboat-participants/members', {:target => '_blank'}
